    "description": "Vortex: The Gateway 是一款开放世界的生存恐怖游戏。<br><br>由于进入了一个神秘的维度旋涡，你将发现自己身处外星世界。为了生存而探索、适应、建设和战斗。每天，你将在不同的时间面对该行星上的各种危险，面对不断变化的气温，饥渴交加。你可以探索景色壮观但险象环生的地方，那儿总是有土生土长的动物不断来袭。<br><br>如果你想活下来，就得保持警惕，小心翼翼，不断建设，英勇作战。同时地球上的生命发生巨大的变化。什么变化呢？通过这场冒险之旅，你将知道一些底细。做最坏的准备吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> story mode: escape from the island<br></li><li> survival mode: protect yourself and your injured friend<br></li><li> a huge, diverse and fully explorable alien island with a unique atmosphere, visuals and emblematic sceneries<br></li><li> non-generated environment, every location was designed by hand<br></li><li> dynamic day-night cycle<br></li><li> crafting system: harvest resources to create equipment by combining them together<br></li><li> building system: build shelters, fences, storage, fire, etc.<br></li><li> survival aspects: hunger, thirst, stamina, health, different temperatures, hiding<br></li><li> living fauna: more than 30 types of harmless and dangerous animals<br></li><li> collect food, water and hunt<br></li><li> some of the story elements are available already<br></li><li> atmospheric music and sounds<br></li><li> Steam achievements</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Inspired by</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> The Forest<br></li><li> Stranded Deep<br></li><li> The Long Dark<br></li><li> 7 Days to Die<br></li><li> Dying Light<br></li><li> Rising World<br></li><li> Subnautica<br></li><li> FarSky</li></ul>",
